title: 154: Are Magicians Actually Cool? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 154
description:
Rhett & Link recall a recent visit to The Magic Castle, a magician with a seemingly endless number of doves in his clothes, and beg the question "are magicians actually cool" in this week's episode of Ear Biscuits.
